      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense but can u be a bit more serious? like i need the actual scientific details for the exam. specifically for anaphase, what is actually pulling them apart? and i think u missed cytokinesis at the end too. can u finish the explanation with more technical terms?",
      "source": "evaluator"
